{"tid":759621,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"[Maths]外星人數野唔會12345咁低B？","createTime":"2018-07-28T19:00:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T21:27:38.000Z","uid":165773,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5b116b4f8432eb39d6ab27885681f5a015b0dc75","tid":759621,"uid":165773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T19:00:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_E2iiuunK-E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_E2iiuunK-E&d=edoxUIiW2rOnmaHAoo5pHMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=384db1fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_E2iiuunK-E</a><br />\n人類社會而家絕大部份情況都係用緊<br />\nℝ（Real number ）同<br />\nℂ （Complex number ）既system<br />\n但係其實仲發展左<br />\nℍ （Quaternion）同<br />\n𝕆 （Octonions）<br />\n不過物理學主流極少理會<br />\n39歲既劍橋大學博士研究生Furey相信<br />\n用𝕆 可以簡化/重新演繹物理學equations<br />\n從而得出對宇宙更深入既推論同理解<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3BZyds_KFWM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3BZyds_KFWM&d=edoxUIiW2rOnmaHAoo5pHMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=121c18d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3BZyds_KFWM</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/29/025406_3653e221b004ad3b79eec35b66e944c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F29%2F025406_3653e221b004ad3b79eec35b66e944c6.jpg&h=33c04750&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.quantamagazine.org/the-octonion-math-that-could-underpin-physics-20180720/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.quantamagazine.org%2Fthe-octonion-math-that-could-underpin-physics-20180720%2F&d=edoxUIiW2rOnmaHAoo5pHMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=bc6060dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.quantamagazine.org/the-octonion-math-that-could-underpin-physics-20180720/</a><br />\n<br />\n數學/物理巴絲點睇？"},{"pid":"539426c4a958bb0e9df2ea9c648d3d91baa8bace","tid":759621,"uid":33213,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTim