d":147721,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T03:31:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>物理學主流極少理會</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n電磁場方程曾經有段時間係用四元數去表述<br />\n物理學家好實際既 有用既數學工具就拎黎用架喇"},{"pid":"cf7f1b4ffc9389dd6611974a700ffc8abde1ebdc","tid":759621,"uid":147009,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T03:36:50.000Z","msg":"quaternion同octonion根本係將cross product valid嘅dimension(3同7) 寫番落scalar form咋嘛 連notation都用埋一樣"},{"pid":"f54821d5432790e408367eebb579803b0efef236","tid":759621,"uid":45169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T09:11:10.000Z","msg":"9 年PHD <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾我一早痴左線"},{"pid":"f4f149e5adfb07a0633e58307fba2979ec712777","tid":759621,"uid":78298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cf7f1b4ffc9389dd6611974a700ffc8abde1ebdc","tid":759621,"uid":147009,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T03:36:50.000Z","msg":"quaternion同octonion根本係將cross product valid嘅dimension(3同7) 寫番落scalar form咋嘛 連notation都用埋一樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T09:54:49.000Z","msg":"怪唔之得咁熟口面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"519eb5f44fc31f5c3c9bce4e35aa407d05e5177e","tid":759621,"uid":147721,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cf7f1b4ffc9389dd6611974a700ffc8abde1ebdc","tid":759621,"uid":147009,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T03:36:50.000Z","msg":"quaternion同octonion根本係將cross product valid嘅dimension(3同7) 寫番落scalar form咋嘛 連notation都用埋一樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T20:55:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://arxiv.org/pdf/1509.00501.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Farxiv.org%2Fpdf%2F1509.00501.pdf&d=edoxUIiW2rOnmaHAoo5pHMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=efafb28e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/pdf/1509.00501.pdf</a><br />\nPage 6 fig 1<br />\n明明係parallel發展 比你講到quaternion同octonion係拎vector既野黎用咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7289d472a4f765df8ce4b0a934712e3ae6b2b348","tid":759621,"uid":112406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T00:39:09.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"b7d1a2192d68dbbbf199104a3cd20ba242c92acf","tid":759621,"uid":82382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T01:05:34.000Z","msg":"高質post 留名學野"},{"pid":"6661a43105d7d2557234e8f2bdff30ff6c74068f","tid":759621,"uid":7840,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T04:18:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a7261fd700e7112855679d0b9e7b3f69e4df109a","tid":759621,"uid":76587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T18:34:17.000Z","msg":"淨係識少少qua <br />\nlm學嘢"},{"pid":"66cf4fdff89589fcc17a7208c31ccfa47d2399f6","tid":759621,"uid":165773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T20:55:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.quantamagazine.org/peter-scholze-becomes-one-of-the-youngest-fields-medalists-ever-20180801/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.quantamagazine.org%2Fpeter-scholze-becomes-one-of-the-youngest-fields-medalists-ever-20180801%2F&d=edoxUIiW2rOnmaHAoo5pHMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=d62f3f3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.quantamagazine.org/peter-scholze-becomes-one-of-the-youngest-fields-medalists-ever-20180801/</a><br />\n仲有呢個p-adic number system<br />\n好似real number 咁<br />\n都係負到正無限<br />\n都係填滿整數之間既gap<br />\n但係特別在<br />\ntwo numbers are considered close not if the difference between them is small, but if that difference is divisible many times by p.<br />\n<br />\n新聞話條友用呢個system簡化左一D舊proof"},{"pid":"cb72810c5144eb20ea4dc02ce2338b398f9754f7","tid":759621,"uid":165773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T21:07:10.000Z","msg":"新聞話..<br />\n透過移動p值<br />\n可以產生一個series of p-adic number systems<br />\n呢個series被稱為perfectoid spaces <br />\n<br />\n透過游走於 perfectoid spaces <br />\n（不同p 值既number system）<br />\n可以極有效搵倒複雜<br />\npolynomials既解<br />\n唔洗做傳統運算<br />\n因為某D p值既systems<br />\n互相轉換係特別方便<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://arxiv.org/abs/1306.2070\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Farxiv.org%2Fabs%2F1306.2070&d=edoxUIiW2rOnmaHAoo5pHMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=e9c901fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://arxiv.org/abs/1306.2070</a>"},{"pid":"8bd681db160bb868c3a65596c787b5795dd9cc83","tid":759621,"uid":165773,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T21:27:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/21txpoJir4g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F21txpoJir4g&d=edoxUIiW2rOnmaHAoo5pHMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=0306c14b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/21txpoJir4g</a><br />\n感覺p-adic 好似<br />\n將Real number睇做一個由好多細ring<br />\n組成既一個大ring（負到正無限）<br />\n每個細ring長度係一個p<br />\n<br />\n咁令極大同極小既數（都係細ring）<br />\n幾何上都好近"}]}